    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or smudge anywhere! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for total perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
