    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. The exterior is finished in its original factory paint, boasting a deep, glass-like luster without a single swirl mark, chip, or imperfection. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather seats are firm and free of any creasing, and the original carpets have been protected since day one. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, having been maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers. It drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered, with crisp shifts and a silent, rattle-free cabin. Every button, sensor, and feature functions perfectly. Included are all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a comprehensive binder of service records. For the collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is the finest example currently available.",
      "price": 46500.0,
