    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this thing since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, like-new ride without the dealership stress, you\u2019ve found it. Come say hi and take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love with it!",
