    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This S54-powered specimen features the legendary 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been professionally overhauled. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring documented preventative subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh utilizing OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers to maintain factory kinematic precision. Mechanically flawless with zero deferred maintenance, this E46 represents the pinnacle of the analog driving experience, free of the typical rod bearing or cooling system vulnerabilities.",
